mainboard.name: Vito, Thorn of the Dusk Rose

decks.notes: The main concept of this deck is to utilize mono black control strategies in order to disrupt the opponent's game plan and dominate the battlefield. By using cards like Duress, Inquisition of Kozilek, and Thoughtseize, the deck aims to strip away the opponent's resources and disrupt their strategy. In addition, the deck includes a variety of removal spells such as Eliminate, Heartless Act, and Toxic Deluge to deal with any threats that the opponent manages to play. The deck also includes powerful win conditions like Sheoldred, the Apocalypse and Liliana of the Veil to close out the game once the opponent has been forced to discard their hand and board presence.
